				<h2>The @mention highlight color in chat is the same as default OS X highlight color</h2>
<p>When I'm mentioned in chat, my name in the person's message is highlighted blue. 99CCFF, to be precise. The problem is, that's exactly the same color as the default OS X highlight color, and I always try to click out of the selection.</p>

<p>I understand this is by design, but in my opinion it should be changed.</p>

<p><img src="https://i.stack.imgur.com/fqG1R.png" alt="Screenshot of name highlight and selection highlight"></p>

<p>(Above: name highlight followed by text highlight)</p>

